_sText: Ok... This is my second map in 3 days. Some info and credits: Mapper: TwixyTwix Screenshots: Sandgrinder + MoH Testing: TwixyTwix Weapons on map: All pistols, smoke grenades and HE grenades Textures: Devolpment textures, also known as ag/dev. Features: funky lights ^^ And a soundscape. and some heat steams. Max players: 24 (12vs12) The houses are whole, so you can go into them :) Else, just enjoy! And if you like much, then add it to your favorites. You are always welcome to vote for me as Mapper of the Month (MaoM). Vote for TwixyTwix Mapper of the month Vote for Crinale.
